dataset_id: Literature-Derived Parameters for the BIOME-BGC Terrestrial Ecosystem Model
title: Literature-Derived Parameters for the BIOME-BGC Terrestrial Ecosystem Model
summary: Various aspects of primary production of a variety of plant species found in natural temperate biomes were compiled from literature and presented for use with process-based ecosystem simulation models or ecosystem studies.  Information was selected according to the input parameter needs of the BIOME-BGC process-based simulation model.
